    "By integrating real-world data from various sources, researchers can enhance the robustness and generalizability of IDS models.",
    "This ensures that they are better equipped to handle the complexities of current and emerging attack vectors while preserving data privacy.",
    "Due to recent advancements in generative models, the use of advanced privacy techniques will likely expand in the coming years to secure federated learning, as shown in Fig. 10.",
